            <div class="timeline-tags">
              <span>Java</span><span>Sybase</span><span>PL/SQL</span><span>Bash</span><span>Git</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-header">
              <h3>Senior Developer</h3>
              <span class="timeline-period">2021 — 2024</span>
            </div>
            <p class="timeline-company">Tenant Evaluation</p>
            <p class="timeline-desc">Full-stack development for tenant screening SaaS. Monolith-to-microservices migration, third-party integrations (Square, Microbilt, Twilio), mentorship, E2E testing.</p>
            <div class="timeline-tags">
