          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-header">
              <h3>Mobile / Backend Developer</h3>
              <span class="timeline-period">2015 — 2021</span>
            </div>
            <p class="timeline-company">Grupo AL · Public Administration</p>
            <p class="timeline-desc">Android + Spring backend for traffic fine management (Gessan Mobile, mCam, misTributos). DGT SOAP integrations, Cordova cross-platform app.</p>
            <div class="timeline-tags">
              <span>Java</span><span>Spring</span><span>Android</span><span>Cordova</span><span>Oracle</span><span>SOAP</span><span>Ionic</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-header">
              <h3>ABAP Developer (Intern)</h3>
              <span class="timeline-period">2014 — 2015</span>
            </div>
            <p class="timeline-company">CEMOSA · Engineering</p>
            <p class="timeline-desc">SAP module development with ABAP IV. Bug fixes in production modules, construction material classification.</p>
            <div class="timeline-tags">
