          <div class="project-tags"><span>TypeScript</span><span>Next.js</span><span>PostgreSQL</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/EnriqueRS/antimolebot" target="_blank" class="project-card">
          <div class="project-icon">🌱</div>
          <h3>AntimoleBot</h3>
